review: 20号京东首发，18点08分11秒下单成功，原以为21号就能收到货，结果居然推迟了一周27号发货。这备货，发货速度真是太坑了！而且没有任何解释和补偿，期间打客服电话也没有用。只能说京东已经不是五年前那个顾客至上的京东了，如今的VIP，钻石，Plus都比不上以前诚意满满的致歉来的暖心！很失望！ 还是说手机吧。上一个手机LG G3也是京东首发入手用了三年多，当年这块首款2k屏幕还是那么通透完美，刷完机依旧流畅，无奈电池最近老是断触，影响工作，不得不考虑换机。 这次入手mate10基本达到心理预期：6+128G价格四千出头，溢价不算高。屏幕分辨率比mate9有所提升，虽然比不了LG的通透，三星的艳丽，但也算是国产机里不错的冷屏了。背面玻璃材质看上去大气精致。要是宽度再稍窄一点，手感就完美了。系统流畅简洁，功能很适合商务使用。莱卡双摄可玩性强。保留红外遥控功能，这个很赞。不足之处，：没有防水功能，音质和外放很一般，续航感觉还可以再提高点，一般使用一天半没问题，全程亮屏使用估计在6个多小时左右，期待新版本优化提升一下吧。

review: 期待已久的亮蓝色，其实64G够我用，不过为了这亮蓝色多花400也值了，坚持快5年的小米2终于退下去了，用了几天，先说说优点，手机真的很漂亮，手感也不错，屏幕亮度高，目前体验系统很流畅，miui的换机功能很好用，直接把系统设置，程序和程序设置转移到新手机，各种应用账号都直接过来了，特别方便，续航目前看中度使用一天够用，没有想象中那么耐用，选米6是因为性能够强，目前看835加6G的配置应该至少能用2年，拍照虚化效果不错，红外遥控器功能好用。 说说不足，重量重，特别容易沾指纹，没找到特别合适的手机壳和贴膜，送的保护套有点松，本身带了个磨砂膜，本来膜的感觉不错，但是非得写了按钮位置和为发烧而生这几个字，没法长时间用非常可惜，成功申请了miui9的内测，感觉不到明显速度提升，增加的功能不错，但是有些改变不完善，其实比起流畅续航我更在乎，开的程序多了剩余内存还是容易到1个G的，所以6G也不是万无一失，玩游戏机身温度有点高，到不是烫，但是明显感觉到有温度，夜间拍照很模糊。 总体来说手机还是很喜欢的，希望能好好用几年，感觉如果不重视蓝颜色，2499的性价比更好。
review_en: Long-awaited bright blue, in fact, enough for me 64G, but for this bright blue 400 spent more value, insisted fast millet 2 5 years finally retreated, spent a few days, first talk about the advantages of mobile phones Really beautiful, feel good, screen brightness, the current system is very smooth experience, miui replacement function is very easy to use, directly to the system settings, procedures and program settings transferred to the new phone, a variety of applications account directly over , Especially convenient, battery life now see the use of a day enough, there is no imagination so durable, the election of rice 6 because the performance is strong, the current configuration to see the 835 plus 6G should be able to use at least 2 years, virtualization effect is good, infrared Remote control function easy to use. Not enough to say, heavy weight, especially easy to dip fingerprints, did not find a particularly suitable mobile phone shell and foil, send the protective cover a little loose, itself with a matte film, the film feels good, but have to write the button position and Fever with these words, can not be used for a long time is a pity that the successful application of miui9 closed beta, did not feel significant speed increase, increase the functionality is good, but some changes are not perfect, in fact, more than smooth life I care more , Open the program more than the remaining memory is still easy to a G, so 6G is not foolproof, play the game a bit high body temperature, not to hot, but obviously felt temperature at night is very vague pictures. Overall mobile phone is still very much like, I hope I can take a few years, I feel if you do not pay attention to the blue color, the price of 2499 better.

review: 最差的一次购物体验，12月1号购买，激活正常使用，由于灯光比较暗，没有发现问题，第二天白天发现右上角做工问题请求换机，客服第一借口说人为造成，眼瞎啊。第二，超过24小时，外观问题不予退换，第三，激活的手机不能退换。很想骂人，我忍。继续和售后交涉，5号下午给我打来电话，说补偿一百代金券，同时又发现问题，赠送的半年碎片险都没有，更不能解我心头之恨，客服向领导申请（多一些补偿，并给予赠送碎屏险服务），耐心等待，4天了还没有回复，9号下午抽空又联系售后，问题没得到解决，告诉我只有100代金券的补偿，别的啥也没有，意思是我活该。说一下自己的想法，京东其实一直很信赖，下面那个是我的账号，一年消费真不少，15年5月的时候在京东买过一个iPhone6的产品，屏幕上面有很明显的一个亮点，找过也是各种问题推脱，没解决，为什么这么大的电商卖手机的价钱比实体店，官网都要低，我分析是这样，电子产品出厂时候就有很严格的质量检验，会把产品分为几个等级（比如ABCD类）作为电商巨头，很有肯能大量的以低价拿到BC类的产品，他们也不敢拿不好的货，A类的都送到实体店，而且真真是7天包退15天包换，这就是行业的潜规则。自述。

review: 价钱相比做工和配置性能是很不错的。下单后很担心有些评论说的二手机，收到后仔细检查，没发现是二手机的痕迹，但竟然已经有贴膜！是别人的退货吗？好忐忑喔！ 预置应用很简洁，连视频和音乐播放器都没有，要自己安装第三方的。系统有一个很重大的遗漏(不是漏洞)，就是用双sim卡时，不能关闭或停用其中一个，这应该是工程师的疏忽，希望后续系统更新能加上这个功能。还有就是没有近场通讯功能，不能充值公交卡，不能当小区门禁卡用。希望联想以后的产品都能加上NFC。

System has a very big omission (not a loophole), that is, with a double sim card, you can not turn off or disable one, which should be the engineer's negligence, hope that follow-up system updates can add this feature. There is no near-field communication capabilities, can not recharge the bus card can not be used when the district card access. Hope that future products can be coupled with NFC.

Specific use of smooth: 3 +64 with MediaTek X10 processor, the configuration in the thousand dollars is not bad, run relatively smooth, if you buy now, I definitely recommend the 4 +64 version. Photography: Have to say, red rice note4 performance in this area, is not very good, photo effects are not flattering ah. Screen: Have to say that the entire cell phone most worth Tucao is this a 5.5-inch screen. Screen resolution is not high, poor display, watch TV drama, there is a strong sense of grainy, remember, is a strong sense of grainy, hard to accept. Above from the appearance and usage, introduced a red rice note4 phone, a thousand dollars more balanced machine, the biggest drawback, I think this is a poor screen quality, the other are relatively good.

review: 1月份出厂的新鲜。谈谈米，这也是品牌顶级系列米了，活动价五折尝试下。东北人不缺所谓好好吃的米，十五年以前不敢说粮店谁便抓都好吃。05年以后品牌包装机械化深加工大米出现。单位定点去米农家采购的行为基本不存在。有口感带饭香的大米难寻了。要么高价赌试，再者应季采购。深加工，订单化，统一米种，导致口味缺失已成定局。谈谈这米看了推荐就下了2单。包装够好，抽真空内面还是锡箔纸非透明，米超级白，米泛生香，个体纤长不均；制饭时飘香，不吃水，制熟米粒净白纤粒，搅拌近闻带有余香，吃食粒明弹软，最大遗憾是没有饭味。好饭是用嘴来品尝的，不是用鼻子吃的。评价生米香气和熟米味是两个概念，评价标准千万别本末倒置。入口咀嚼弹软压候味蕾回香这才是好味道，五分饭香这米顶多二点五分饭味。原因估计抛光太严重，米粒个体基本上属于中号纤体，有可能受限于有机两字，有机者不上肥料长不大长不饱满托词。有机，五常，稻花香，层层加码，但用喉舌体量独缺失饭味。有些评价总是煮粥煮粥的，好气，就是年底扶贫米陈米煮成粥都好喝，煮个粥香都算成好米标准那就太低了。跟家人吃了两顿这米，吃饭时都是默默无语，不提产地不说品种不提价钱。跟学时放榜后低头情景重现。

This time to buy again, would like to know whether it really said. First, the speed of transport increased, the last time spent more than 48 hours, this time in 48 hours. So I do not know why. The reason why the cold storage is good because of timely delivery. If more than 48 hours is certainly still an old problem. Third, the weight is still not enough. Two kilograms of net weight of his package, but with the box is two kilograms, remove the carton only 1800 grams, which is more pit? If this package how consumers can determine the net shrimp weight? Fourth, health problems, once said aquaculture water quality may not be good, there are processing problems, this time found that shrimp black less than half. But still there. So it is not well and completely improved and solved. The most terrible is to eat a few with a taste of disinfectant shrimp. Is this for cleaning? Fifth, spicy flavor is still OK, the original said spicy flavor may have capsaicin added, the spicy flavor does not seem so single. Possible formulations have been adjusted. In short, the lack of weight is very bad mood, the actual number of a bag of 37 shrimp, step on the line only.

review: 手机总体来说还不错，运行流畅，还有很多特色功能，比如说分屏，除此之外，还有主打的拍照与音乐功能都很好用，我比较喜欢拍照的快慢镜头，挺好玩的，音乐播放感觉也挺好，还有指纹解锁，挺灵敏的，这几点手机本身的功能我觉得很赞！再说手机厂商的特别服务，手机出厂都贴好钢化膜，贴的都很好，省了我很多功夫，而且自带透明软胶套，方便很多事，难怪这手机卖的这么好，的确用心为用户考虑了。最后说一下我一点点的不满意，首先是屏幕，720P的分辨率，看着总感觉有液晶屏的小块块，不是那么细腻；其次是硬件配置，联发科的处理器加LPDDR3内存emmc存储，接近2000的售价，性价比不高；第三是包装，京东自己塑封的，给人感觉有点倒手的感觉。总结一下，手机使用体验感觉不错，正常使用很流畅，电力续航也不错，手机价格波动不大，而且全国统一价，线上线下买都差不多，买到手不会有掉价太快的痛苦，如果对手机要求不是太多，仅从实用性来讲，这款手机挺不错的。
review_en: Mobile phones are generally good, smooth operation, there are many features, such as split-screen, in addition, there are the main photo and music functions are very good, I prefer to take pictures of the camera, very fun , Music playback is also very good, there are fingerprints unlock, very sensitive, these phone functions I feel very good! Besides the special services of cell phone manufacturers, cell phone factory posted good steel film, paste are good, save me a lot of effort, and comes with a transparent soft cover, easy to do many things, no wonder this phone to sell so good, really hard User considered. Finally, I am a little bit of dissatisfaction, the first is the screen, 720P resolution, watching the total feel of small pieces of LCD screen, not so delicate; followed by the hardware configuration, MediaTek processor plus LPDDR3 memory emmc storage, Close to the price of 2000, the price is not high; the third is the packaging, Jingdong their own plastic, giving people feel a little hands down feeling. To sum up, the mobile phone experience feels good, the normal use is very smooth, power life is not bad, mobile phone price fluctuations, and the national uniform price, online and offline to buy are similar, buy the hand will not have the plunge too painful, if Phone requirements are not too many, only from the practical terms, this phone is very good.

review: 颜值超美，黑色息屏一体性很棒，不过听说蓝色更漂亮？舍友有一台蓝色荣耀八，也挺漂亮的。屏幕是这台手机最大的短板了，拖动字体发绿，耗电大，实际亮屏时间不足6小时，我很郁闷官方6.5小时阴阳师怎么来的？充电慢，一个半小时只能充满80%。续航100-0花费22小时，实际亮屏时间不足六小时。不过我企鹅和微信后台一直挂着，估计是这两个比较耗电。指纹秒解，支持zfb指纹付款，微信不支持。系统流畅度还是可以的，感觉开应用的速度比6s还快，但是过渡动画不够ios丝滑，应该是过渡动画帧率不如ios高的缘故。不过华为的500天不卡顿可能就是吹牛了，用了几天切换应用的时候卡顿了一下，不知道是不是刚开机的缘故？相机拍照太鲜艳了，特别是红和绿，太假了。内存和闪存都测试了，ddr4ram,ufs2.1rom,这点还是比较满意的。不过我刚买的时候测770，用了几天测就580多了，不懂是不是因为装了应用才变慢的？最后还是要吐槽一下京东，标配版可以抢购但每次都是订单失败？所以我只买到了套装，加一年碎屏险。感觉有点贵。这台手机如果*买到还是挺有性价比的，除了屏幕和相机一般外，其他都是不错的，特别是系统响应速度挺快的。
review_en: Beautiful value of the United States, black screen integration is great, but I heard blue more beautiful? Roommate has a blue glory eight, but also very beautiful. The screen is the biggest shortcomings of this phone, drag the font green, power consumption, the actual time less than 6 hours bright screen, I am very depressed official 6.5 hours yin and yang division came? Charge slowly, a half hour can only be full of 80%. Life 100-0 spent 22 hours, the actual bright screen less than six hours. However, my penguin and WeChat have been hanging from the background, it is estimated that these two more power. Fingerprint second solution, support zfb fingerprint payment, WeChat does not support. System fluency is still possible, I feel faster than 6s open the application faster, but the transitional animation is not enough silky, it should be transitional animation frame rate as ios high reason. However, Huawei 500 days without Caton may be bragging, spent a few days when switching applications Caton a bit, I do not know is not just boot reason? Photo camera too bright, especially red and green, too fake. Memory and flash are tested, ddr4ram, ufs2.1rom, this point is still quite satisfactory. However, when I just bought the test 770, spent a few days measuring more than 580, do not know is not installed because it slowed down? Finally, Tucao about Jingdong, the standard version can buy but every time the order failed? So I only got the package, plus one year broken screen insurance. Feel a bit expensive. This phone if you buy is still quite cost-effective, in addition to the screen and the camera in general, the other is good, especially the system response speed very fast.

review: 我是京东商城的老顾客了，但是发现京东商城现在越来越差，让我很寒心，有几点我极其不满，首先邮费变了，以前39包邮，现在突然该到了59？？第二，以前买书买什么都有全品图书满300减100或者满400减200，现在不仅全部都限制，而且就连今年六一少儿图书满200减100也不是全品~~第三点，自从不同的卖家入驻，购物中就带来了很大的不便利，比如买不同卖家的商品就不停的加邮费，前两年也没有这样，购物方便快捷，我想问问大家京东到底怎么了，要闹哪样啊？？ 问题补充：举例说明，今年六一，我想帮同事买《冒险小虎队》，京东推出的活动是图书满200减100，这套书分为4个系列，和在一起买就400多，分开买每个系列就100多，京东自己的小算盘打得也太好了吧，买400多的一套就可以享受满200减100，分开拼3个分系列就没有任何优惠~~~刚才我还忘了说一点，第四，京东商城上积分机制明显是我不喜欢的机制，以前书评我还可以给好评，因为有积分，现在搞了个不伦不类的京豆，还能抽奖，这个获奖概率有多少？真正让消费者实惠的奖又有多少~~？？为什么京东就不能把做广告的那些钱为消费者做些实事？？ sam没牙猫 2014-06
review_en: I am an old customer Jingdong Mall, but found that Jingdong Mall is getting worse, so I am chilling, I am extremely dissatisfied with a few points, the first postage has changed, before the 39 package, and now it suddenly came to 59? ? Second, before buying a book to buy what has a full book full 300 minus 100 or 400 minus 200, and now not only all are limited, but even this year 61 Children's Books over 200 minus 100 is not all ~ ~ Third, since different Of the sellers settled in the shopping has brought great inconvenience, such as buying different sellers of goods on non-stop plus postage, the first two years did not, shopping convenient, I would like to ask everyone Jingdong in the end how, What should I do? ? I would like to help my colleagues to buy "Adventure Little Tigers" this June. The activity launched by Jingdong is that the book is over 200 minus 100. This book is divided into four series, and together with the purchase of more than 400 separate Buy each series to more than 100, Jingdong own little abacus playing too well, buy a set of more than 400 can enjoy over 200 by 100, separate fight 3 sub-series there is no discount ~ ~ ~ I just Also forgot to say that, Fourth, the integration mechanism Jingdong Mall obviously I do not like the mechanism, before the book reviews I can give praise, because there are points, and now engaged in a nondescript Peking, but also lucky draw, the winning probability how many? Really allow consumers affordable prize how much ~ ~? ? Why Jingdong can not advertise the money to do something practical for consumers? ? sam no teeth cat 2014-06

Flash Mate9 is also the second and second prize, V9 may be drawn to EMMC. Spent a week, comment on the next: 1. Flash second prize, minus one star. Prior to worry about the resolution of 1080P small screen on the 5.9, in fact, very comfortable with. 2. Prior to the use of glory 6P, night screen that glare, Mate9 is very smart, adjust the brightness according to the light is very suitable for glasses. 3. Lycra camera is really good, a little SLR feeling 4. 4 + 32 configuration, in this era of excess cell phone performance, there can still be a daily surplus 1.7G shipped, as memory, 32G, my idea is Feel less can add a memory card on OK, forget it, 32G 2719 into, cheaper than the 4 +64 700, you can buy a lot of memory card! 5. Personal replacement is very important reason is to play the king glory, with friends Millet MIX Xiaolong 821 than loading him for a few seconds faster. 6. One hour to get the battery charge, one day a charge, 5 o'clock in the afternoon left a 30% off work, quite satisfactory. 7. Huawei Forum said the wifi cut-off, yellow screen and other issues, individuals have not found. In short, the overall quality of this machine at this price is still quite high, no obvious short board! !

review: 11.11下单mate 9 4G 32G手机，今天11.12日拿到安装应用发现，无线（wifi）断续特别严重，家里宽带200M，看了视频，惨不忍睹的停顿，后来找最典型的大流量持续测试，选择了百度地图，下载时几乎停滞状态，下载断续的同时，机器卡顿很严重，在同一荣耀无线路由器pro，对比了荣耀7 ，最慢时截图也有2.9M，高速冲到15M/秒，相差太大，申请退货。 期间联系了华为客户，第一次恢复网络设置，第二次建议调整APN、WLAN+等，第三次说是无线路由器MAC地址过滤问题（顶级荒唐的客户水平，所有IP设备全球唯一MAC地址，你华为自己的无线路由器就把自己的手机mac过滤了），听信后再换TP-LINK无限路由器，故障依旧。 乔布斯去世一直用华为手机，前后6个型号了，质量还真不错，开始以为个别机器问题，网上一查，mate 9 无线断流从16年新品上市就开始了，口说无凭，看看百度地图同时下载广东省的地图做个比较，mate 9 停止在93B/秒，荣耀7是2.9M/S！ 如果有0分，愿意送给华为mate 9一万个！

Steve Jobs has been using Huawei's mobile phone, before and after the 6 models, the quality is really good, began to think that the problem of individual machines, online check, mate 9 wireless cut-off from the 16 new market began, saying no virtue, take a look at Baidu Map at the same time to download the map of Guangdong Province to be compared, mate 9 stop at 93B / second, glory 7 is 2.9M / S! review: #SOAP R11 千元全面屏#9月27日入手，总结这款手机的优缺点，供大家参考。 先说优点： 1.与一般5.5寸手机同样平面尺寸下容纳了5.7寸屏幕。 2.手机非常省电，把玩半天消耗40%左右的电量，正常使用一天没有问题。 3.发热量低，使用安兔兔进行稳定性测试15分钟，电池温度34.5℃，摄像头位置微热。 4.内存3G+存储32G，内置的软件几乎都可以卸载，非常纯净。 5.日常使用运行速度良好，开启应用与骁龙835机型差距较大，但单独使用时不感觉慢。 6.做工中规中矩，随机自带柔性手机套和塑料屏幕贴膜。 再说缺点： 1.5.7寸屏幕分辨率低，只有1440*720，用惯2K或1080P屏幕后，会有颗粒感，尤其白底黑字场景下。 2.CPU配置较低，采用骁龙430，由于是给老人使用，对大型游戏没有进行测试。 3.相机较渣，前置后置的拍照效果与宣传有较大出入，不如数年前的魅蓝note2拍的细致。 4.系统完成度较差，如不能使用第三方桌面，桌面图标大小不可调节，可下载主题、字体都比较少。 5.指纹识别率非常低，正常录入指纹后，使用指纹解锁失败率很高，还需图案或密码解锁。 6.机身较厚(8.34mm)较重(165g)，无快充功能。 最后附上软件测试评分：安兔兔41969，鲁大师性能评测62197，鲁大师体验评测119.41。
review_en: # SOAP R11 thousand full screen # September 27 start, sum up the advantages and disadvantages of this phone for your reference. Let me talk about the advantages: 1. With the same general 5.5-inch mobile phone size to accommodate the 5.7-inch screen. 2. The phone is very power-saving, playing a half-day consumption of about 40% of the electricity, the normal use of a day no problem. 3. Low calorie, the use of security Bunny stability test for 15 minutes, the battery temperature 34.5 ℃, the camera location slightly hot. 4. Memory 3G + storage 32G, built-in software can be almost uninstall, very pure. 5. Daily use The running speed is good, open the application and the Snapdragon 835 models a large gap, but when used alone do not feel slow. 6. workmanship quite satisfactory, comes with a random flexible phone cover and plastic screen film. Besides disadvantages: 1.5.7-inch screen resolution is low, only 1440 * 720, used to 2K or 1080P screen, there will be grainy, especially in black and white scenes. 2.CPU configuration is lower, the use of Snapdragon 430, because it is for the elderly to use, not to test large-scale games. 3. The camera is more slag, front and back of the photo effects and publicity have a greater discrepancy, not as good as a few years ago Charm blue note2 shot detail. 4. Poor system performance, such as the third-party desktop can not be used, the desktop icon size can not be adjusted, can download the theme, fonts are less. 5. Fingerprint recognition rate is very low, the normal fingerprints, the use of fingerprint to unlock a high failure rate, but also pattern or password to unlock. 6. Thicker body (8.34mm) heavier (165g), no fast charge function. Finally, attach the software test score: Ann Bunny 41969, Lu master performance evaluation 62197, Master Lu experience evaluation 119.41.

review: 给三星是因为，第三方卖的的手机真的有猫腻！之前看过一些评论，说耗电大的，速度慢的！好吧，这里我给大家一个答案：这家第三方卖的这款小米5c，是手机圈子里那种出厂预装一堆垃圾APP的手机。但你可以放心，手机是新的，这一点我亲自去了小米之家验证的。工程师坦言，这就是315曝光的那种预装灰色产业链的那种手机。作为一个稍微懂点技术的米粉，开机时我就有疑虑，因为并没有MIUI的初始化设置过程，直接进入主界面。而且应用商店居然是腾讯和搜狗的！安全中心是腾讯的，浏览器是UC！我靠，一个大杂烩，根本不是原生MIUI！问商家客服，对方的解释跟复读机一样“我家卖的就是原装新机”，态度极其不清不楚的，应该是心知肚明却又不能承认而已。所以，只能在官网申请解锁，直接线刷，才一切清净了！所以那些觉得小米不快的，去找个懂行的朋友把手机线刷成官方纯净的MIUI系统吧！
review_en: To Samsung is because the third party to sell the phone really tricky! Read some comments before that power-hungry, slow! Well, here I give you an answer: This third-party to sell this millet 5c, is the cell phone circle that factory pre-installed a bunch of garbage APP phone. But you can rest assured that the phone is new, which I personally went to verify the millet home. The engineer admitted that this is the kind of exposure of the 315 pre-installed gray chain that kind of cell phone. As a little technical point of rice, I have doubts boot, because there is no MIUI initialization setup process, directly into the main interface. And the application store is actually Tencent and Sogou! Security Center is Tencent, the browser is UC! I rely on, a hodgepodge, is not native MIUI! Asked the business customer service, the other's explanation with the repeater as "my family is selling original machine", attitude is extremely unclear, it should be well aware but can not recognize it. So, can only apply for unlock in the official website, direct line brush, only clean everything! So those who feel millet unpleasant, to find a knowledgeable friend to the phone line into the official pure MIUI system!

review: 第一次用中兴努比亚手机，我是用了差不多9天才来评价的。 先说优点：1，充电快，3100毫安电池，电量从0%到100%，只用了65分钟充满。感觉充电很给力；2，手机拍照感觉相当不错，手机照相功能完胜苹果，和华为莱卡双摄像头照出来的效果都不差（去年用的华为p9）；3，手机绑定的程序软件，不想用直接可以删除，不影响手机使用；4，全面屏的效果真的很棒；5，和同功能手机相比，价格实惠一些；6，物流给力，上午下单下午到货，感觉不错；7，新机安卓系统都很快，这个就不用多说了。 缺点：1，手机没有专用的耳机插孔，带耳机线还得通过插到转接头，然后插到充电插孔上，很麻烦；2，蓝牙4.1耳机连接不上努比亚手机，很郁闷；3，右侧音量按键和息屏功能键固定不牢靠，很松动，咔擦咔擦响，让人质疑做工粗糙；4，感觉手机稍微有点厚。 总结一下，相对我来说，总体感觉还是不错。
review_en: The first time I used Netsia Nobile phone, I spent almost 9 days to evaluate. First advantage: 1, fast charging, 3100 mA battery, power from 0% to 100%, only 65 minutes full. Feel charging is awesome; 2, cell phone camera feels quite good, cell phone camera victory over Apple, and Huawei Lycra dual camera according to the results are not bad (last year with Huawei p9); 3, cell phone bundled program software, do not want to use Can be directly deleted, does not affect the use of mobile phones; 4, the effect of a full screen really great; 5, and functional phones compared to the price of some; 6, logistics force, afternoon orders afternoon arrival, New Android system is very fast, this needless to say. Disadvantages: 1, the phone does not have a dedicated headphone jack, headphone cable also had to plug into the adapter, and then plug into the charging jack, a lot of trouble; 2, Bluetooth 4.1 headphone not connect Nubian mobile phone, very depressed; 3, the right volume buttons and interest-free screen function keys fixed is not solid, it is loose, click wiping the clatter, people questioned the rough workmanship; 4, feeling a little bit thick cell phone. To sum up, relative to me, the overall feeling is good.

review_en: The first time with Sharp's phone, the overall feeling is still very good, specifically to talk about: 1. The screen is very clear, Sharp itself to do this, the effect of natural good; 2. Fingerprint identification Soon, recognition is very high, the basic as long as you can confirm the finger before. Said that the point is not satisfied: 1. Why the edge of the screen is not circular chamfer for the hypotenuse, with the overall style does not take; 2. In addition, due to the thin body, no headphone jack, only charging jack and public, it seems only with a Bluetooth headset. Overall is still very good, the price of 2499 compared to this configuration is not worth it.
